    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em>Incompatible with other conversions</em></p>\n<p>You heavily modify your lightweapon to allow you to make a ranged weapon attack. With this modification, you can make a ranged weapon attack with a range of 30/60. On a hit, it deals [[/r 1d6]] energy damage.</p>\n<p>Additionally, when you make your first attack on your turn, you can alter the properties of your modified lightsaber. Until the start of your next turn, the damage type of your modified lightsaber is changed to ion. </p>\n<p>You can use this trait a number of times equal to your Intelligence modifier (a minimum of once). You regain all expended uses when you complete a short or long rest.</p>",
